data.description: Huge price reduction. Motivated sellers. Updated, comfortable home in wine country where you can enjoy sitting on the covered porch overlooking your small homestead Fenced, x-fenced, a little over 8ac with a winter creek on the lower property. The land has pastures/open spaces, plenty of land for growing food or commercial crops (check county zoning regs), more. Two big barns were previously used for horses, hay storage & equip. The home has been remodeled and totally customized! Shown by appt only.
